# Angular Project Structure

## Core Application Files
- [src/app/app.ts](mdc:src/app/app.ts) - Main application component
- [src/app/app.html](mdc:src/app/app.html) - Main application template
- [src/app/app.css](mdc:src/app/app.css) - Main application styles

## Configuration and Routing
- [src/app/app.config.ts](mdc:src/app/app.config.ts) - Application configuration
- [src/app/app.routes.ts](mdc:src/app/app.routes.ts) - Client-side routing
- [src/app/app.config.server.ts](mdc:src/app/app.config.server.ts) - Server configuration
- [src/app/app.routes.server.ts](mdc:src/app/app.routes.server.ts) - Server-side routing

## Entry Points
- [src/main.ts](mdc:src/main.ts) - Client-side entry point
- [src/main.server.ts](mdc:src/main.server.ts) - Server-side entry point
- [src/index.html](mdc:src/index.html) - Main HTML template

## Testing
- [src/app/app.spec.ts](mdc:src/app/app.spec.ts) - Component tests

